WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.904 align:middle line:90%
[THEME MUSIC]

00:00:03.904 --> 00:00:19.040 align:middle line:90%


00:00:19.040 --> 00:00:21.290 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA MEREDITH: Dr. Linda
Backman is back with us

00:00:21.290 --> 00:00:24.170 align:middle line:84%
to plunge deeper into the
concept of soul essence

00:00:24.170 --> 00:00:25.200 align:middle line:90%
psychology.

00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:26.840 align:middle line:84%
This means that we
examine our lives

00:00:26.840 --> 00:00:28.890 align:middle line:84%
through the lens
of our past lives,

00:00:28.890 --> 00:00:31.740 align:middle line:84%
our soul's origin, and
our life's purpose.

00:00:31.740 --> 00:00:33.890 align:middle line:84%
This also takes into
account the family

00:00:33.890 --> 00:00:37.820 align:middle line:84%
we choose to incarnate into and
all of those dynamics, which

00:00:37.820 --> 00:00:39.202 align:middle line:90%
is a very complex topic.

00:00:39.202 --> 00:00:40.410 align:middle line:90%
We're going to get into that.

00:00:40.410 --> 00:00:42.600 align:middle line:84%
So, first of all,
it's wonderful.

00:00:42.600 --> 00:00:44.160 align:middle line:84%
Wonderful to have
you back again.

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:49.800 align:middle line:84%
And I love this topic of soul
incarnation, family incarnation,

00:00:49.800 --> 00:00:53.100 align:middle line:84%
dynamics, and how
these soul families,

00:00:53.100 --> 00:00:55.850 align:middle line:84%
our soul families choose
to come back together

00:00:55.850 --> 00:00:59.540 align:middle line:84%
to continue lessons
and torture each other

00:00:59.540 --> 00:01:01.780 align:middle line:90%
and enchant each other.

00:01:01.780 --> 00:01:04.280 align:middle line:84%
>> LINDA BACKMAN: Struggle
and love all at the same time.

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:09.410 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And just to lay the
foundation for this, tell us--

00:01:09.410 --> 00:01:12.230 align:middle line:84%
I mean, people know you from
my past interviews with you.

00:01:12.230 --> 00:01:13.970 align:middle line:84%
So we won't go into
all the history.

00:01:13.970 --> 00:01:17.740 align:middle line:84%
But you've been doing
regression work, psychotherapist

00:01:17.740 --> 00:01:19.130 align:middle line:90%
for a very long time.

00:01:19.130 --> 00:01:25.660 align:middle line:84%
And so let's talk about why
you feel it's so important, so

00:01:25.660 --> 00:01:28.930 align:middle line:84%
valuable for a person to
have some understanding

00:01:28.930 --> 00:01:32.530 align:middle line:90%
of their past lives.

00:01:32.530 --> 00:01:35.020 align:middle line:84%
And is it necessary
for everyone?

00:01:35.020 --> 00:01:37.580 align:middle line:10%
>> LINDA: Well, that's
a great question.

00:01:37.580 --> 00:01:41.350 align:middle line:10%
And sometimes people will say to
me, well, Linda, my past lives

00:01:41.350 --> 00:01:44.510 align:middle line:10%
are past, so why do I need
to know about my past lives?

00:01:44.510 --> 00:01:48.610 align:middle line:10%
But the bottom line is our past
lives show up in current life,

00:01:48.610 --> 00:01:51.620 align:middle line:10%
and our past lives tell
us what kind of work--

00:01:51.620 --> 00:01:54.820 align:middle line:10%
not work, not paid
work, but what kind

00:01:54.820 --> 00:01:57.580 align:middle line:10%
of accomplishments
and learning has

00:01:57.580 --> 00:02:01.370 align:middle line:10%
been going on lifetime
to lifetime to lifetime?

00:02:01.370 --> 00:02:05.300 align:middle line:84%
It explains, well, why do
I feel drawn to this person

00:02:05.300 --> 00:02:06.680 align:middle line:90%
but I've never met them?

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:08.240 align:middle line:90%
Why do I have this skill?

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:09.680 align:middle line:90%
Where did it come from?

00:02:09.680 --> 00:02:11.720 align:middle line:90%
What have I accomplished before?

00:02:11.720 --> 00:02:14.540 align:middle line:84%
And so our past lives are
part of our current life.

00:02:14.540 --> 00:02:16.010 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah, absolutely.

00:02:16.010 --> 00:02:17.980 align:middle line:84%
So one of the things
I love is what

00:02:17.980 --> 00:02:20.650 align:middle line:84%
I talked about
early on, which is

00:02:20.650 --> 00:02:25.690 align:middle line:84%
the notion that a soul carefully
plans their incarnations.

00:02:25.690 --> 00:02:27.580 align:middle line:84%
And a lot of people
have a problem

00:02:27.580 --> 00:02:31.720 align:middle line:84%
with this concept, which is
I happen to agree with you.

00:02:31.720 --> 00:02:35.740 align:middle line:84%
My understanding is that we
definitely choose our families

00:02:35.740 --> 00:02:36.980 align:middle line:90%
before birth.

00:02:36.980 --> 00:02:39.880 align:middle line:84%
We're not just stuffed into
a body against our will

00:02:39.880 --> 00:02:43.490 align:middle line:84%
with a bunch of strangers, even
if we'd like to say we were,

00:02:43.490 --> 00:02:46.420 align:middle line:90%
even if it wasn't fun.

00:02:46.420 --> 00:02:48.920 align:middle line:84%
Let's talk about that
in a fuller sense.

00:02:48.920 --> 00:02:51.864 align:middle line:84%
>> LINDA: Well I
like to call this--

00:02:51.864 --> 00:02:54.260 align:middle line:84%
you referred to soul
essence psychology.

00:02:54.260 --> 00:02:56.590 align:middle line:84%
So soul essence
psychology means,

00:02:56.590 --> 00:02:58.400 align:middle line:90%
who am I at that core level?

00:02:58.400 --> 00:02:59.570 align:middle line:90%
Who have I been before?

00:02:59.570 --> 00:03:00.970 align:middle line:90%
Where do I come from?

00:03:00.970 --> 00:03:02.060 align:middle line:90%
Why am I here now?

00:03:02.060 --> 00:03:05.290 align:middle line:84%
So when we step
into our families,

00:03:05.290 --> 00:03:08.080 align:middle line:84%
that's not to say that every
family member is someone

00:03:08.080 --> 00:03:09.670 align:middle line:90%
we've had many lives with.

00:03:09.670 --> 00:03:15.910 align:middle line:84%
But almost always generally
those first-degree relatives are

00:03:15.910 --> 00:03:16.992 align:middle line:90%
souls we've--

00:03:16.992 --> 00:03:18.200 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Known before, yeah.

00:03:18.200 --> 00:03:19.617 align:middle line:84%
>> LINDA: That
we've known before.

00:03:19.617 --> 00:03:25.300 align:middle line:84%
And we're either cleaning
something up from the past.

00:03:25.300 --> 00:03:28.390 align:middle line:84%
One of the tricky parts
is that both souls have--

00:03:28.390 --> 00:03:30.970 align:middle line:84%
both people in body,
both souls in body

00:03:30.970 --> 00:03:33.110 align:middle line:84%
have to agree to
clean things up.

00:03:33.110 --> 00:03:37.490 align:middle line:84%
So sometimes we don't clean
things up in current life.

00:03:37.490 --> 00:03:42.322 align:middle line:84%
That's because both people
aren't ready to do that.

00:03:42.322 --> 00:03:45.940 align:middle line:84%
But yes, the
familiarity we have is,

00:03:45.940 --> 00:03:47.930 align:middle line:84%
oh, I mean, it
could be a mentor.

00:03:47.930 --> 00:03:49.640 align:middle line:84%
It could be your
next door neighbor.

00:03:49.640 --> 00:03:52.840 align:middle line:84%
It's like, why do I feel
drawn to this person?

00:03:52.840 --> 00:03:54.915 align:middle line:84%
It's usually because
you've known them before.

00:03:54.915 --> 00:03:57.960 align:middle line:90%


00:03:57.960 --> 00:04:00.600 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: I had a situation in
my life where someone very dear

00:04:00.600 --> 00:04:03.460 align:middle line:84%
passed and I was left
with the impression, God,

00:04:03.460 --> 00:04:06.240 align:middle line:84%
I wish I could have done
more for them before they

00:04:06.240 --> 00:04:07.090 align:middle line:90%
passed away.

00:04:07.090 --> 00:04:09.160 align:middle line:90%
I feel like I didn't.

00:04:09.160 --> 00:04:11.230 align:middle line:84%
And so I talked
with my own group--

00:04:11.230 --> 00:04:15.160 align:middle line:84%
my own soul group, and
they explained to me,

00:04:15.160 --> 00:04:18.540 align:middle line:84%
they said, you don't
understand this correctly.

00:04:18.540 --> 00:04:20.640 align:middle line:90%
You helped this soul before.

00:04:20.640 --> 00:04:24.360 align:middle line:84%
And this soul was here to help
you along in this lifetime

00:04:24.360 --> 00:04:27.330 align:middle line:84%
and wasn't able to accomplish
what they came to do.

00:04:27.330 --> 00:04:29.550 align:middle line:84%
And it was very
interesting because they

00:04:29.550 --> 00:04:33.550 align:middle line:84%
said the time for this
connection has now passed.

00:04:33.550 --> 00:04:36.090 align:middle line:90%
You will not be together again.

00:04:36.090 --> 00:04:39.480 align:middle line:84%
You can be thankful and
grateful and love this soul,

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:44.070 align:middle line:84%
but the soul will go on and
continue learning this lesson

00:04:44.070 --> 00:04:46.465 align:middle line:84%
with someone else
who's in the space

00:04:46.465 --> 00:04:48.840 align:middle line:84%
to learn that lesson because
I guess I must have moved on

00:04:48.840 --> 00:04:49.960 align:middle line:90%
from that lesson.

00:04:49.960 --> 00:04:52.090 align:middle line:84%
And I thought that
was interesting,

00:04:52.090 --> 00:04:55.720 align:middle line:84%
because a character who
I've incarnated with plenty,

00:04:55.720 --> 00:04:59.510 align:middle line:84%
and they said, now
time's up on that one.

00:04:59.510 --> 00:05:00.950 align:middle line:84%
It was fascinating
because that's

00:05:00.950 --> 00:05:02.867 align:middle line:84%
the only time I've heard
that where you're not

00:05:02.867 --> 00:05:05.040 align:middle line:90%
going to see them again.

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:07.640 align:middle line:90%
>> LINDA: I think there are--

00:05:07.640 --> 00:05:08.850 align:middle line:90%
how to say this.

00:05:08.850 --> 00:05:12.440 align:middle line:84%
It's like the spiritual realm
is much more complicated

00:05:12.440 --> 00:05:13.790 align:middle line:90%
than people think.

00:05:13.790 --> 00:05:17.550 align:middle line:84%
And so it's like, how
do plans get made?

00:05:17.550 --> 00:05:20.160 align:middle line:84%
How do plans, you
might say, get unmade?

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:22.522 align:middle line:90%
Referring to what you just said.

00:05:22.522 --> 00:05:23.777 align:middle line:90%
And what's the point?

00:05:23.777 --> 00:05:25.610 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Because you
just said that earlier

00:05:25.610 --> 00:05:29.250 align:middle line:84%
that both souls have to show
up to learn the thing together.

00:05:29.250 --> 00:05:30.890 align:middle line:90%
That's why I brought it up.

00:05:30.890 --> 00:05:33.110 align:middle line:90%
Didn't happen that way.

00:05:33.110 --> 00:05:34.640 align:middle line:90%
>> LINDA: Exactly.

00:05:34.640 --> 00:05:38.070 align:middle line:84%
But yes, the spiritual
realm can decide,

00:05:38.070 --> 00:05:41.400 align:middle line:84%
well, OK, it didn't work
this way to clean this up.

00:05:41.400 --> 00:05:44.660 align:middle line:90%
So we'll create another way.

00:05:44.660 --> 00:05:47.360 align:middle line:84%
It's almost like,
to some extent,

00:05:47.360 --> 00:05:48.960 align:middle line:90%
it's a little bit experimenting.

00:05:48.960 --> 00:05:50.910 align:middle line:90%
It's like, this didn't work.

00:05:50.910 --> 00:05:52.533 align:middle line:90%
So let's try something else.

00:05:52.533 --> 00:05:54.200 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Just stuck
with the same souls

00:05:54.200 --> 00:05:58.180 align:middle line:84%
where you have any kind
of inequity in your desire

00:05:58.180 --> 00:06:00.748 align:middle line:84%
to learn, your ability to
take on challenge and change.

00:06:00.748 --> 00:06:03.040 align:middle line:84%
You're not still stuck with
it if you don't work it out

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:04.540 align:middle line:90%
with that soul.

00:06:04.540 --> 00:06:06.260 align:middle line:90%
>> LINDA: Totally.

00:06:06.260 --> 00:06:10.390 align:middle line:84%
Here's a different version
of that or a different story.

00:06:10.390 --> 00:06:12.920 align:middle line:90%
This is about me personally.

00:06:12.920 --> 00:06:15.950 align:middle line:84%
I have a very dear, long
standing girlfriend.

00:06:15.950 --> 00:06:18.220 align:middle line:84%
I've known her since
I think I was 12.

00:06:18.220 --> 00:06:20.660 align:middle line:90%
And we're very different today.

00:06:20.660 --> 00:06:23.930 align:middle line:84%
Everybody that's listening
knows me and knows what I do.

00:06:23.930 --> 00:06:27.790 align:middle line:84%
She does not believe
in this type of work.

00:06:27.790 --> 00:06:32.180 align:middle line:84%
She's very tied to
her own Western--

00:06:32.180 --> 00:06:35.150 align:middle line:84%
you might say Western
religious beliefs,

00:06:35.150 --> 00:06:36.860 align:middle line:90%
which is completely fine.

00:06:36.860 --> 00:06:39.640 align:middle line:90%
I totally respect her for that.

00:06:39.640 --> 00:06:42.060 align:middle line:84%
In a way, we're walking
different paths and in a way

00:06:42.060 --> 00:06:42.860 align:middle line:90%
we're not.

00:06:42.860 --> 00:06:45.140 align:middle line:90%
We're still very good friends.

00:06:45.140 --> 00:06:48.200 align:middle line:84%
I don't know that we're
cleaning up a lot of things,

00:06:48.200 --> 00:06:52.480 align:middle line:84%
but what I'm speaking
to is where people--

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:55.750 align:middle line:84%
where we accept, OK, I have
this perspective of life.

00:06:55.750 --> 00:06:57.460 align:middle line:84%
I have this spiritual
perspective.

00:06:57.460 --> 00:07:00.130 align:middle line:84%
Somebody else has a
different perspective.

00:07:00.130 --> 00:07:02.620 align:middle line:84%
Does that mean we
can't interact?

00:07:02.620 --> 00:07:05.650 align:middle line:84%
Does that mean it's not
purposeful to be connected?

00:07:05.650 --> 00:07:08.140 align:middle line:84%
My sense is no, it
doesn't mean that.

00:07:08.140 --> 00:07:11.400 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Oh, yeah, that's
what I find, because like you,

00:07:11.400 --> 00:07:14.400 align:middle line:84%
are there people who have
certainly judged my career path

00:07:14.400 --> 00:07:16.540 align:middle line:90%
over the last 25 years or so?

00:07:16.540 --> 00:07:19.500 align:middle line:84%
And most of the
people in my life

00:07:19.500 --> 00:07:22.110 align:middle line:84%
just didn't understand why
I would use my media career

00:07:22.110 --> 00:07:23.862 align:middle line:90%
and do that with it.

00:07:23.862 --> 00:07:25.660 align:middle line:90%
But these are people I love.

00:07:25.660 --> 00:07:29.640 align:middle line:84%
And so I just choose to
connect with them in the areas

00:07:29.640 --> 00:07:32.430 align:middle line:84%
where we actually
have connection.

00:07:32.430 --> 00:07:36.400 align:middle line:84%
So if it's about our children,
if it's about movies,

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:39.070 align:middle line:84%
you can still connect and
you can still have love.

00:07:39.070 --> 00:07:40.740 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't mean you
have to be on-- this

00:07:40.740 --> 00:07:42.060 align:middle line:90%
is a big one right now.

00:07:42.060 --> 00:07:44.460 align:middle line:90%
This is huge in society.

00:07:44.460 --> 00:07:48.220 align:middle line:84%
You don't have to believe the
same to still love one another.

00:07:48.220 --> 00:07:51.450 align:middle line:84%
>> LINDA: And I think, I
mean, I love how we just segue

00:07:51.450 --> 00:07:53.600 align:middle line:90%
into different pieces of this.

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:55.880 align:middle line:84%
Makes me think about
how many of my clients

00:07:55.880 --> 00:07:59.100 align:middle line:84%
come and they bring questions
to their regression.

00:07:59.100 --> 00:08:01.620 align:middle line:84%
And one of their questions,
especially if they're a mom,

00:08:01.620 --> 00:08:03.750 align:middle line:84%
they'll say, well, how
can I help my child?

00:08:03.750 --> 00:08:06.740 align:middle line:84%
How can I-- and the child
might be seven or the child

00:08:06.740 --> 00:08:08.190 align:middle line:90%
might be 47.

00:08:08.190 --> 00:08:09.290 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't really matter.

00:08:09.290 --> 00:08:11.190 align:middle line:90%
But, what can I do?

00:08:11.190 --> 00:08:14.060 align:middle line:84%
My child is struggling
with x, y, z.

00:08:14.060 --> 00:08:16.910 align:middle line:84%
And almost always the
guides of the client

00:08:16.910 --> 00:08:22.170 align:middle line:84%
will say your child's on their
journey, you're on your journey.

00:08:22.170 --> 00:08:25.580 align:middle line:84%
And the guides
often will say, let

00:08:25.580 --> 00:08:30.180 align:middle line:84%
your child make their choices,
love them, support them.

00:08:30.180 --> 00:08:34.289 align:middle line:84%
And it's so hard when
it's your own child,

00:08:34.289 --> 00:08:36.799 align:middle line:84%
but let them walk
their own journey.

00:08:36.799 --> 00:08:39.140 align:middle line:90%
But love them all the same.

00:08:39.140 --> 00:08:40.320 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:41.789 align:middle line:90%
And I know that one well.

00:08:41.789 --> 00:08:45.950 align:middle line:84%
And so let's talk
about that for a moment

00:08:45.950 --> 00:08:49.280 align:middle line:84%
because there is a thing
that's been happening-- there

00:08:49.280 --> 00:08:50.510 align:middle line:90%
are articles written on it.

00:08:50.510 --> 00:08:54.880 align:middle line:84%
And they label it more of a
millennial generation thing,

00:08:54.880 --> 00:08:57.240 align:middle line:84%
but it's probably
in the Zs as well.

00:08:57.240 --> 00:08:58.480 align:middle line:90%
Gen Z, the Zoomers.

00:08:58.480 --> 00:09:02.500 align:middle line:84%
And that is a rejection
of parents and family,

00:09:02.500 --> 00:09:05.160 align:middle line:84%
which is becoming
fairly prominent.

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:06.930 align:middle line:84%
I'm shocked at the
number of people

00:09:06.930 --> 00:09:10.140 align:middle line:84%
I run across whose
kids have said,

00:09:10.140 --> 00:09:14.830 align:middle line:84%
I don't accept the way you do
something or you talk to me

00:09:14.830 --> 00:09:18.130 align:middle line:84%
and I want to sever ties with
you because you stress me out.

00:09:18.130 --> 00:09:21.630 align:middle line:84%
And what is going
on there to have

00:09:21.630 --> 00:09:27.450 align:middle line:84%
so much more a mass movement
towards severing ties

00:09:27.450 --> 00:09:29.350 align:middle line:90%
with family or parents?

00:09:29.350 --> 00:09:32.880 align:middle line:84%
Have you seen any of
this in your regressions?

00:09:32.880 --> 00:09:34.710 align:middle line:90%
>> LINDA: I mean, I don't see--

00:09:34.710 --> 00:09:36.960 align:middle line:84%
I certainly know what you're
talking about in terms

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:38.708 align:middle line:90%
of severing ties.

00:09:38.708 --> 00:09:39.750 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So many people.

00:09:39.750 --> 00:09:41.483 align:middle line:90%
And that never used to happen.

00:09:41.483 --> 00:09:43.150 align:middle line:84%
You might not like
your parents, per se.

00:09:43.150 --> 00:09:44.770 align:middle line:90%
You might find them whatever.

00:09:44.770 --> 00:09:46.330 align:middle line:90%
But you didn't sever ties.

00:09:46.330 --> 00:09:47.950 align:middle line:90%
They were your parents.

00:09:47.950 --> 00:09:49.240 align:middle line:90%
>> LINDA: Well, yes.

00:09:49.240 --> 00:09:50.690 align:middle line:90%
But I think it's almost--

00:09:50.690 --> 00:09:52.830 align:middle line:90%
some of that's generational.

00:09:52.830 --> 00:09:56.030 align:middle line:84%
Obviously, one or
two generations ago,

00:09:56.030 --> 00:09:57.600 align:middle line:90%
who ever heard of divorce?

00:09:57.600 --> 00:09:58.740 align:middle line:90%
It just didn't happen.

00:09:58.740 --> 00:10:01.450 align:middle line:90%
People just stayed together.

00:10:01.450 --> 00:10:02.700 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Except in my family.

00:10:02.700 --> 00:10:04.347 align:middle line:90%
My grandfather did it a lot.

